{"tid":2265462,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"暖男爸爸丨鄭中基新劇現抗爭對白被封神劇 監製︰多謝香港人","createTime":"2020-10-31T12:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T14:19:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"421f9313136a2494983bf089a09bce491f75cc13","tid":2265462,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"由鄭中基、張可頤主演的ViuTV劇集《暖男爸爸》，開播首星期以來獲不少觀眾、網民激讚，當中在去年經常聽到的抗爭字句、抵死貼地的對白亦令人感受至深。對於被封為神劇，監製兼導演及編劇的戚家基（Peter）表示︰「呢個係香港人嘅故事，所以要多謝香港人。」<br />\n<br />\n《暖》劇播出以來有不少迴響，對此監製Peter表示︰「拍《暖》劇嘅初衷係畀香港人睇，會有共鳴，希望啲人一聽就覺得係香港人講嘅說話。呢個劇喺2020年拍，呢啲對白就係平時我哋喺街度聽到。好似聯繫咗connect咗，而家唔會仲有人講隨機應變，香港人同香港人之間梗係講be water啦，呢段時間講開嘅，就係呢啲對白。」對於網民、觀眾都喜歡《暖》劇，Peter十分感恩，他說︰「多謝所有喜歡呢個劇嘅人，你哋令參與創作嘅人好感動，我哋喺疫情中開拍，多謝劇組成員大家一齊出生入死。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201031/JMTEV4KD6ZAD5HE53G3WULLKZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201031%2FJMTEV4KD6ZAD5HE53G3WULLKZQ%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0UsakxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=51647792\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201031%2FJMTEV4KD6ZAD5HE53G3WULLKZQ%2F&h=918080ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201031/JMTEV4KD6ZAD5HE53G3WULLKZQ/</a>"},{"pid":"897383094af4effb015e3f68c923c54572a33fa9","tid":2265462,"uid":61161,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"